_:N36f31dfb855f4695a6edd3fccba9ce93 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Lucy Rigby MP was appointed as Chief Secretary to the Treasury on 14 May 2026.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Parliamentary Secretary (Economic Secretary to the Treasury) at HM Treasury from 6 September 2025 to 14 May 2026 and Solicitor General between 2 December 2024 and 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Northampton North in July 2024.</p>\n" .
